maccarthy , desmond the court theatre , 1904 - 1907 ; a commentary and criticism   the mexican film las troyanas ( 1963 ) directed by sergio véjar , adapted by writer miguel angel garibay and véjar , is faithful to the greek text and setting ; ofelia guilmain portrays hecuba , the black&white photography is by agustín jimenez .

